¶ La-la la-la la-la-la ¶

35:07.172 --> 35:10.440
¶ La-la la-la la-la la-la ¶

35:10.442 --> 35:12.676
-Hi. -Hi!

35:12.678 --> 35:15.445
[gasps] Ah, the horses.

35:15.447 --> 35:17.347
Oh, well... Okay.

35:17.349 --> 35:19.149
Wait, there's two of it!

35:19.151 --> 35:20.884
[laughing] Oh, perfect!

35:22.154 --> 35:24.154
Oh, yeah.

35:24.156 --> 35:25.288
It's beautiful.

35:25.290 --> 35:26.523
[laughing]

35:26.525 --> 35:28.391
[snarling]

35:28.393 --> 35:29.860
-These shoes. -Oh, yeah.

35:29.862 --> 35:32.162
'Cause I... Uh, hello?

35:32.898 --> 35:34.431
-Hey. -Oh...

35:39.204 --> 35:40.437
[vehicles honking]

35:42.207 --> 35:43.406
-[clattering] -[gasps]

35:43.408 --> 35:45.242
[Sadie laughing]

35:45.244 --> 35:47.310
[indistinct chatter]

35:49.515 --> 35:52.215
-That'd be 22.36. -Okay.

35:52.217 --> 35:53.850
-Thank you, Sadie. -Of course.

35:53.852 --> 35:55.886
[music continues]

35:55.888 --> 35:59.189
Wish me and my sister got along as well as you two.

35:59.191 --> 36:01.291
Yeah, we're very lucky.

36:01.293 --> 36:03.160
[vocalization]

36:04.463 --> 36:07.564
¶ La-la la-la la-la-la ¶

36:07.566 --> 36:09.633
¶ La la la la la la... ¶

36:11.503 --> 36:12.769
[door chimes chiming]

36:14.473 --> 36:16.206
Nicole.

36:16.208 --> 36:17.340
Whoa. Sadie.

36:17.342 --> 36:18.441
-Oh... -[laughing]

36:18.443 --> 36:19.809
Hey!

36:21.647 --> 36:25.315
I never realized how much you guys look like each other.

36:25.317 --> 36:26.683
-Mm-hmm. -Ah.

36:26.685 --> 36:30.387
[chuckles] How was school today?

36:30.389 --> 36:33.290
It was a nightmare, I seriously almost slapped Serena

36:33.292 --> 36:34.624
to get suspended.

36:34.626 --> 36:36.626
Ha! That's amazing.

36:36.628 --> 36:38.395
Come on, let's go.

36:39.765 --> 36:40.964
So did you skip out of school early?

36:40.966 --> 36:44.267
Uh-uh. Wednesday's a half day.

36:44.269 --> 36:45.602
Hey, we still going to the movie?

36:45.604 --> 36:48.405
Yeah. We could just go over there now.

36:48.407 --> 36:50.207
Play some pinball while we wait.

36:50.209 --> 36:52.275
Oh, does The Old Mill still have pinball machines?

36:52.277 --> 36:53.577
-That's right. -What?

36:53.579 --> 36:54.811
You're pretty good at it, aren't you?

36:54.813 --> 36:56.780
I'm really good at it.

36:56.782 --> 36:59.516
But, uh, I don't think I'm gonna come with you.

36:59.518 --> 37:02.452
-Because I don't feel great. -What's wrong?

37:02.454 --> 37:03.787
Nothin', I'm just kinda like headache-y

37:03.789 --> 37:06.356
and, you know, nauseous.

37:06.358 --> 37:08.692
-We could go home. -No, you guys go to the movies.

37:08.694 --> 37:10.894
I'll go home for a bit and then, like, I'll pick you up after?

37:10.896 --> 37:12.929
Yeah, okay, if that's okay with you.

37:12.931 --> 37:14.798
Yeah, it's totally fine. Just text me.

37:14.800 --> 37:15.932
-Okay. -Okay.

37:15.934 --> 37:19.269
-We'll miss you. -Love you. Bye.

37:19.271 --> 37:22.339
-Feel better. -[Sadie] I will.

37:23.842 --> 37:26.243
Why is she trying to look like you?

37:26.245 --> 37:27.911
Don't you think that's weird?

37:27.913 --> 37:30.747
No. I think it's cool.

37:30.749 --> 37:32.015
Come on.

37:33.685 --> 37:35.452
Come on. Ah.

37:44.730 --> 37:45.762
[Derek] Nicole!

37:45.764 --> 37:48.832
[dramatic music]

38:07.419 --> 38:10.320
Hey! What are you doing?

38:12.658 --> 38:14.057
Nicole!

38:18.463 --> 38:21.531
[music continues]

38:24.369 --> 38:25.735
Hello?

38:37.316 --> 38:38.481
Hey.

38:45.924 --> 38:47.924
[groans] Sadie, I'm sorry.

38:47.926 --> 38:50.360
I, I thought you were Nicole.

38:52.798 --> 38:53.930
[exhales]

38:57.402 --> 38:58.768
A...

39:02.607 --> 39:05.075
-I've never done this before. -Uh...

39:05.077 --> 39:08.044
But I want to, with you.

39:10.882 --> 39:13.450
You won't tell anyone, right?

39:13.452 --> 39:15.719
At school? I-I just don't wanna get a reputation.

39:15.721 --> 39:17.954
It would break my mother's heart.

39:17.956 --> 39:19.689
N-no. I...

39:19.691 --> 39:21.491
-I-I won't tell anyone. -Okay.

39:21.493 --> 39:24.561
[dramatic music]

39:26.832 --> 39:28.398
[Sadie] Is this your first time?

39:28.400 --> 39:31.101
[both breathing heavily]

39:38.910 --> 39:40.677
Derek?

39:41.079 --> 39:44.147
Shh...

39:57.429 --> 39:58.928
[door shuts]

40:01.900 --> 40:04.934
-Anyone home? -[Sadie sobbing]

40:11.009 --> 40:12.475
Nicole?

40:13.512 --> 40:15.912
Nicole? Honey, what's wrong?

40:16.782 --> 40:18.882
[sobbing]

40:20.085 --> 40:22.585
Nicole wanted to give me a haircut

40:22.587 --> 40:24.654
so we'd be twins.

40:24.656 --> 40:27.090
So you wanna, you wanna tell me what's wrong?

40:27.092 --> 40:30.960
I'm gonna be 26 next week!

40:31.897 --> 40:34.731
[sobbing] It's not funny!

40:34.733 --> 40:36.599
Hey. Hey, hey, hey.

40:36.601 --> 40:39.636
We can celebrate yours and Nicole's birthday together.

40:39.638 --> 40:40.870
The same time, like we used to.

40:40.872 --> 40:43.807
No, Nicole wants her own party.

40:43.809 --> 40:47.911
Uh, no. She adores you.

40:47.913 --> 40:51.714
I can't remember the last time it was just you and me.

40:51.716 --> 40:54.617
[groans] I love you.

40:54.619 --> 40:56.686
I love you, too!

40:58.190 --> 41:00.790
-[sobbing] -Always.

41:05.130 --> 41:06.930
-Bad TV? -Mm.

41:06.932 --> 41:09.032
-Yeah, bad TV. -Mm-hmm?

41:09.034 --> 41:12.001
-Chinese food from Twin Dragons? -I want Chinese food.

41:12.003 --> 41:13.803
All right, well, I'll go order.

41:13.805 --> 41:16.139
I'm old! [sobbing]

41:16.141 --> 41:18.541
Oh, my God. Those shoes are hideous.

41:18.543 --> 41:21.010
Look how different her nose is in this season...

41:21.012 --> 41:22.045
Wait...

41:22.047 --> 41:23.546
[indistinct chatter]

41:25.183 --> 41:27.484
Right? Like, they say it's not scripted.

41:27.486 --> 41:28.785
But it's clearly...

41:28.787 --> 41:30.854
I thought you were gonna pick us up.

41:32.724 --> 41:34.891
Yeah, I thought you were gonna text me.

41:34.893 --> 41:37.227
Your phone is right there! I texted you multiple times.

41:37.229 --> 41:38.828
Did you really?

41:39.831 --> 41:42.131
Oh, shit! Nicole, I'm sorry!

